antz |first=Jason |access-date=22 December 2019 |date=18 December 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191219150435/https://mynorthwest.com/1643654/rantz-10-best-films-2019/ |archive-date=19 December 2019 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n* 3rd{{snd}} Mara Reinstein, ''[[Us Weekly]]''<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.usmagazine.com/entertainment/pictures/top-10-movies-of-2019-us-best-films-of-the-year/|title=Top Movies of 2019: 'Hustlers,' 'Avengers: Endgame' and More|last=Reinstein|first=Mara|work=US Weekly|date=6 December 2019|access-date=15 December 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191209153256/https://www.usmagazine.com/entertainment/pictures/top-10-movies-of-2019-us-best-films-of-the-year/|archive-date=9 December 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n* 3rd{{snd}} Chuck Yarborough, ''[[Cleveland Plain Dealer]]''<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.cleveland.com/life-and-culture/g66l-2019/12/03381814fc64/rocketman-tolkien-1917-among-years-best-chuck-yarborough-pd-critics-picks-2019.html |title='Rocketman,' 'Tolkien,' '1917' among year's best: Chuck Yarborough PD critics' picks 2019 |last=Yarborough |first=Chuck |work=Cleveland Plain Dealer |date=23 December 2019 |access-date=24 December 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191224191919/https://www.cleveland.com/life-and-culture/g66l-2019/12/03381814fc64/rocketman-tolkien-1917-among-years-best-chuck-yarborough-pd-critics-picks-2019.html |archive-date=24 December 2019 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n* 4th{{snd}} Lindsey Bahr, ''[[Associated Press]]''<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://apnews.com/0ec356ee3fa4dcdd71683d966cb4f5ba|title='Once Upon a Time,' 'Portrait' top AP's 2019 best films list|date=5 December 2019|website=AP NEWS|access-date=15 December 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191210015305/https://apnews.com/0ec356ee3fa4dcdd71683d966cb4f5ba|archive-date=10 December 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n* 4th{{snd}} Benjamin Lee, ''[[The Guardian]]''<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2019/dec/17/best-films-2019-us-no-4-1917 |title=The 50 best films of 2019 in the US: No 4 \u2013 1917 |last=Lee |first=Benjamin |work=The Guardian |access-date=22 December 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191218124144/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2019/dec/17/best-films-2019-us-no-4-1917 |archive-date=18 December 2019 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n* 4th{{snd}} Brian Truitt, ''[[USA Today]]''<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/entertainment/movies/2019/12/03/best-movies-2019-ranked-including-jojo-rabbit-marriage-story/4322043002/|title=The 10 best movies of 2019 definitively ranked, from 'Avengers: Endgame' to 'Jojo Rabbit'|first=Brian|last=Truitt|website=USA TODAY|access-date=15 December 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191216013901/https://www.usatoday.com/story/entertainment/movies/2019/12/03/best-movies-2019-ranked-including-jojo-rabbit-marriage-story/4322043002/|archive-date=16 December 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n* 5th{{snd}} Staff consensus, ''[[Consequence of Sound]]''<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://consequenceofsound.net/2019/12/top-25-films-of-2019/|title=Top 25 Films of 2019|date=9 December 2019|access-date=15 December 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191210163111/https://consequenceofsound.net/2019/12/top-25-films-of-2019/|archive-date=10 December 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n* 5th{{snd}} Bruce Miller, ''[[Sioux City Journal]]''<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://siouxcityjournal.com/entertainment/movies/the-best-films-of-hollywood-marriage-story-and-parasite-top/article_34d62ec9-0f99-55b5-8c2d-18dc8692e5c3.html|title=The Best Films of 2019: 'Hollywood,' 'Marriage Story' and 'Parasite' top list|first=Bruce|last=Miller|website=Sioux City Journal|access-date=23 December 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191223203144/https://siouxcityjournal.com/entertainment/movies/the-best-films-of-hollywood-marriage-story-and-parasite-top/article_34d62ec9-0f99-55b5-8c2d-18dc8692e5c3.html|archive-date=23 De